<head>ENGAGEMENT</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">關心</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>THINK DILIGENTLY ABOUT THINGS DESIRING INTENSELY TO IMPROVE THEM. [read like French engagement]</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>The history of engagement in Chinese literature is a promising topic for discussion. As is the question of public space. It is not clear to me what the word would be for "engagement".</p>
        </div>
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>???</p>
        </div>
